{
  "stem": "24615.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had a whip.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started whipping us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told us to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it was a little farm, maybe a half a block, not even half a block away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went-- we went back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the Ukrainian, he asked us, you know, where we went, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had a big stick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, a lot of times he used to hit us over the head, wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He hit us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hid myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they didn't come looking for me, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, you know, they picked the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right then, they knew the names from the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They picked them out, and they made a council-- a Jewish-- a Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they wanted people to go to work, they went to the Jewish council, and they said they needed 15 or 20 Jews to go to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, and they had to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them, they-- they came back, and some of them were killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it depends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, they called me to work too, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was going on, you know, til they made the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it took about 4, 5, 6, or 8, maybe 10 months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it's about 50, 52 years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- but after-- after, I think, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before the ghetto-- you know, so my mother died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was, I think, two weeks, maybe a month before, you know, because a lot of times, she didn't let me go to work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even the Judenrat, you know, you know, sent [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
